===Letter===
'''כ''' (spelled ''[[kaph]]'') is the eleventh letter of the [[Hebrew]] alphabet.<br>
'''ך''' is the final form of the letter ([[sofeet]]), used only at the end of a word.

כ also represents the [[numeral]] 20 in Hebrew numbering.

* '''Last''': [[י]]
* '''Next''': [[ל]]

